{"tid":1420573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論]810大埔遊行戰術討論","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:40:02.000Z","uid":34342,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1d8fe95a88693cc43e45e85468e3fcaef229f6b7","tid":1420573,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:04:13.000Z","msg":"見到好多人屌大埔友，對於下禮拜安排先講琴日大埔戰線利弊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">利：</span><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\">大埔自己友多</span>吹行雞會有好多人，詳見琴日集會，好多街坊支持<br />\n<br />\n2.大埔戰線<span style=\"font-size: large;\">私人屋苑平台多</span>，自己友守住可作反包抄，制高點，急救休息站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">弊</span><br />\n1. 太多和理非，好多淨係識企，明顯<span style=\"font-size: large;\">未夠lv.</span>，要物資冇物資鏈，連手勢都未識做<br />\n<br />\n2. 太多<span style=\"font-size: large;\">自己人false alarm</span>，琴晚無啦啦有條友話新興花園條橋有狗，啲人即刻狗衝散哂 （屌，啲狗由下午已經係條橋啦，都冇狗郁就怕）<br />\n<br />\n3. 大埔人真係比較淆，一有事即跑走，令到<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中前線空晒</span><br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: large;\">難撤退</span>大埔中心要撤退，要行幾遠去太和先走到 （大埔墟近少少，但好易俾狗圍）<br />\n<br />\n利申：大埔友，真心覺得下次等狗出就走，啲場地，戰友，完全不宜久戰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街叫咪死差婆，含撚都嫌你口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2fcf74dd714554f6587227357216e10dd42a34","tid":1420573,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"19bd94abac329d22bb9aff487f1122050d4c5abc","tid":1420573,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9e79d598ab17dd5a69225256f43f966705459a9","tid":1420573,"uid":50362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"大埔我覺得人都係唔夠<br />\n尋日我都係北區過黎 唔少人都係同車一齊落太和"},{"pid":"5e7a8fbad4db58d726c561063fc7e35c15aab4d8","tid":1420573,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d156eeaf1c1e66525e0478346dfc62c9159d530","tid":1420573,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e79d598ab17dd5a69225256f43f966705459a9","tid":1420573,"uid":50362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"大埔我覺得人都係唔夠<br />\n尋日我都係北區過黎 唔少人都係同車一齊落太和"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:41:56.000Z","msg":"好多人show up,但留唔留，上唔上前線就........."},{"pid":"b48a075c514dc3bbd0605ee2e77258d27219bc3e","tid":1420573,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea78a0ce9dd123b8bc50f057648b8cbbd64e5a88","tid":1420573,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"一定要夠多人, 同前線夠FULL GEAR<br />\n<br />\n「廣福村跨河直篤黑警屎忽」呢招未有人用...."},{"pid":"8174b7c04db75b785cb88d7b2f776fba3c64cb45","tid":1420573,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"民建聯大埔支部：<br />\n<br />\n新界大埔寶鄉街112號二樓<br />\n大埔昌運中心商場二樓119B號舖<br />\n大埔太和邨麗和樓121號地下"},{"pid":"173b661533b61351058523ce111a390c29ba8a47","tid":1420573,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我，我係大埔人，本身大埔搞野我唔會割席<br />\n尋日都食左催淚煙<br />\n我只係覺得唔明點解612之後一直都係搞周末及民居<br />\n我係德輔道中返工，等左好耐都無人入來<br />\n日日好似平行時空咁睇住班權貴正常生活<br />\n就算搞中區都係金鐘龍和道果邊完全人無我地打工黃絲掩護<br />\n而搞大埔其實真係完全無用而且影響到自己人<br />\n對斷絕中共資金沒絲毫作用<br />\n可唔可解釋點解要周末搞民居區一至五去中環"},{"pid":"04fb752a632576b6cb0f55ec9ccd7402dbc043d3","tid":1420573,"uid":73649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"天橋。好重要！"},{"pid":"e98b9e05a91a85f22412d126de8eef192a7cc94f","tid":1420573,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日日勇武大家會厭，大埔友區來引到狗清場咪要自己友食煙。而且班狗又懶過閪，唔搞佢佢當無野 和理咪得囉 唔好成日覺得要勇武先有聲音<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a1f4f9adbc21ad95876f9df117e3107dc0ee8365","tid":1420573,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"大埔投石彈弓完全零作用<br />\n<br />\n要檢討"},{"pid":"06374e60a7264e1790261cd05784f2982c94c853","tid":1420573,"uid":15855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:32:33.000Z","msg":"大埔係和理非主場 星期一人係多 但唔會衝<br />\n結果畀狗扔tg 反而搞到義士變救人<br />\n<br />\n星期六咁撚熱又有熱帶氣旋 空氣污染又差 玩 去完就走<br />\n撚下狗 撚狗上到成身gear  仲要封晒路 仲叫街市唔好開門<br />\n玩場大反差 街坊look出動！"},{"pid":"4df6793bc42c7e208350533de968f299cac95e0f","tid":1420573,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3329cae3407b4822628a55ee197932e74defd1","tid":1420573,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf20cc0a5cf8e4989188c803b23db0c465c284d","tid":1420573,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b436bfd7fb3780d326041e3518b6b1da41cbae","tid":1420573,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0621328d5c90f8448ba64908067fa6065b957e9c","tid":1420573,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6e8148c54e1b6523098c2b20a24fdc7dfcbfbb","tid":1420573,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/d9FuaeF.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd9FuaeF.jpg&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnDk5r7V16zLo